  <data key="d17">ards being dried up or consumed. On like manner there are two reasons, for which a subject may not be bound to obey his superior in all things. First on account of the command of a higher power. For as a gloss says on Romans 13:2 , "They that resist [ Vulgate : 'He that resisteth'] the p</data>
