  <data key="d16">structural_editorial</data>
  <data key="d17">God is a mortal sin , because it is contrary to the love of God . Again, the commandments of God contain the precept of obedience to superiors. Wherefore also disobedience to the commands of a superior is a mortal sin , as being contrary to the love of God , according to Romans 13:2 , "He</data>
