  <data key="d15">st.ii-ii.q106.a004.resp</data>
  <data key="d16">explicit_textual</data>
  <data key="d17">Just as in conferring a favor two things are to be considered, namely, the affection of the heart and the gift , so also must these things be considered in repaying the favor. As regards the affection of the heart, repayment should be made at once, wherefore S</data>
  <data key="d18"></data>
  <data key="d19">reviewed_structural_editorial</data>
</edge>
