  <data key="d16">explicit_textual</data>
  <data key="d17">rious degrees corresponding in their order to the things required for gratitude. The first of these is to recognize the favor received, the second to express one's appreciation and thanks, and the third to repay the favor at a suitable place and time according to one's means. And sinc</data>
